criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  American Society Anesthesia I, II；

          -  Age between 3 months and 12 years;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  allergy to anesthetic and analgesic drugs;

          -  history of neuromuscular;

          -  renal, neurological, hepatic disease;

          -  cardiopulmonary diseases;

          -  bradycardia
